Text-TFIDF version 0.01
========================

An implementation of the TF-IDF measure for a collection of text documents.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

none

